## Deliverables — المخرجات

1. **Custom design profile** — per-client design tokens/theme (direction `{{ design_direction }}`) overriding Dealix defaults, inheriting the Dealix forbidden-copy guard.
2. **Custom structure blueprint** — modules, data model, workflows, and the 11 governance gates baked in by construction.
3. **Complete bilingual internal-system specification** (AR primary + EN) — "كامل وشامل".
4. **14-section Proof Pack** with a computed proof score (target ≥ **{{ proof_score_target }}**).
5. **At least one Capital Ledger asset** (custom_design_profile / structure_blueprint / system_spec).
6. Bilingual handoff session walking through the spec and the governance gates.

