## Exclusions — الاستثناءات

This engagement **explicitly does not** include any of the following constitutional non-negotiables:

{% for item in exclusions %}- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

The 11 non-negotiables enforced by code:

1. No scraping of websites, social platforms, or third-party UIs.
2. No cold WhatsApp messaging or WhatsApp automation without recorded opt-in.
3. No LinkedIn automation.
4. No source-less claims; every number or quote requires a Source Passport.
5. No guaranteed-outcome language.
6. No PII in application logs, friction logs, or telemetry.
7. No source-less knowledge answers.
8. No external action (send, charge, publish, share) without explicit logged human approval.
9. No autonomous workflow without a registered agent identity.
10. No project closure without a 14-section Proof Pack with a computed score.
11. No project closure without at least one reusable Capital Ledger asset.

**No full white-label.** The custom system is built for {{ customer_name }}'s internal use; it does not grant Dealix-brand resale rights.

